		{
			description: [
				"&fCenturies ago, humanity had reached the &bThermal Singularity&f. Energy was free, machines thought for us, and matter was nothing but a toy."
				" "
				"&fThen, the &c\"Great Freeze\"&f arrived. In a second, conductivity dropped to zero. Circuits fried, factories froze, and knowledge evaporated into the industrial cold."
				" "
				"&fYou wake up in the ruins of this ancient world. Your mission is not just to survive, but to &6rebuild the chain of knowledge&f. From stone to steam, from steam to the atom."
				" "
				"&e&nYour objective:&r&f Breathe life back into technology. But beware... nature has reclaimed its rights, and it won't be tamed so easily."
			]
			id: "0505D6A0280E26B1"
			rewards: [{
				count: 2
				id: "3F180A36EAE11707"
				item: "croptopia:grilled_cheese"
				type: "item"
			}]
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "&8The Collapse of the Singularity"
			tasks: [{
				id: "48A64927BAA43517"
				title: "&7&lHistory Fragment"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			x: 0.5d
			y: -1.5d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["0505D6A0280E26B1"]
			description: [
				"&fIn this world, cooperation is possible, but protection is vital."
				" "
				"&6&l1. Create your Team:&r"
				"&fOpen your inventory and click the &b\"My Team\"&f icon (top left). This allows you to invite friends and share your quests."
				" "
				"&6&l2. Claim your Chunks:&r"
				"&fClick the &aMap&f icon. &eLeft-click&f the squares to \"Claim\" a territory (no one can break your blocks or open your chests)."
				" "
				"&6&l3. Chunk Loading:&r"
				"&fPress &eShift + Left-click&f on a claimed chunk to keep it active even when you are away. Very useful for your &2Age 2&f machines to keep running!"
			]
			id: "1CC29CFD9D4298A1"
