			dependencies: ["3DA3D8B38A1CA66F"]
			description: [
				"&fIn this pack, knowledge is your best weapon. Here are the basic commands to navigate the interface:"
				" "
				"&6&lOn an item in inventory or JEI:&r"
				"&e- [R] Key:&f Shows the &bRecipe&f of the item."
				"&e- [U] Key:&f Shows the &dUses&f of the item."
				"&e- [A] Key:&f &6Pins&f the item to the left of the screen (very useful for tracking long crafts)."
				" "
				"&6&lInventory Management:&r"
				"&e- [Ctrl] + Click:&f (If configured) moves all identical items."
				"&e- [Space] Key:&f In the JEI search bar to clear your search."
				" "
				"&7&oTip: If you are looking for a specific mod in JEI, type \"@\" followed by the mod name (ex: @powah).&r"
